=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e34511c1ceaa75ee028028c866334b0f6dfa37","tid":216202,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸野都好搶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢出多排降價啦</blockquote><br />\n岩岩出都等？呢家無貨喎巴打 <br />\n你等囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370ea7c7a7718d5966363788a75c13afdbfd2f5f","tid":216202,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/tWwWLTQ5FiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtWwWLTQ5FiQ&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=227b58e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tWwWLTQ5FiQ</a><br />\n睇落粗用就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁既價錢俾個Gimbal你都唔好有太高要求<br />\n<br />\n依家d器材咁平民化，拍片撚無藉口唔鑽研剪片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個價錢算係咁<br />\n鬼佬試落同DJI 差唔幾嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbd2dc1584bafe31e305596b942bb95452cb1a3","tid":216202,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:05:05.000Z","msg":"樓主可唔可以加我tg 有啲野想問下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/pullofyourcar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fpullofyourcar&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=92d2b93d\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/pullofyourcar</a>"}]}